@prefix : <https://bytestar.org/ontology/bytestar-runtime#> .
@prefix bs: <https://bytestar.org/ontology/bytestar-core#> .
@prefix xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> .
@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .

<https://bytestar.org/ontology/bytestar-runtime>
  a owl:Ontology ;
  owl:imports <https://bytestar.org/ontology/bytestar-core> ;
  rdfs:label "ByteStar Runtime Physics" ;
  rdfs:comment "Core pinning, L1 residency, let-it-crash discipline, SPSC topology." .

### Core pinning & soft silicon
:Core a owl:Class .
:hasPinnedCore a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain bs:ByteActor ; rdfs:range :Core .
:coreId a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain :Core ; rdfs:range xsd:nonNegativeInteger .
:exclusivePinning a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain :Core ; rdfs:range xsd:boolean .

### L1 residency guarantee
:L1Residency a owl:Class .
:l1HoldsKernels a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain :L1Residency ; rdfs:range xsd:boolean .
:l1HoldsMPHF    a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain :L1Residency ; rdfs:range xsd:boolean .
:l1HoldsEnvelope a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain :L1Residency ; rdfs:range xsd:boolean .
:hasL1Profile a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain bs:ByteActor ; rdfs:range :L1Residency .

### Let-it-crash semantics
:LetItCrash a owl:Class .
:hasSemantics a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain bs:ByteActor ; rdfs:range :LetItCrash .
:noRuntimeGuards a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain :LetItCrash ; rdfs:range xsd:boolean .
:noDefensiveBranching a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain :LetItCrash ; rdfs:range xsd:boolean .

### SPSC ring topology
:SPSC a owl:Class .
:connects a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain :SPSC ; rdfs:range bs:ByteActor .
:producer a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain :SPSC ; rdfs:range bs:Subsystem .
:consumer a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain :SPSC ; rdfs:range bs:Subsystem .
:constantTimeOps a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain :SPSC ; rdfs:range xsd:boolean .